# Contact Form Aura

Contact Form Aura is a modern, lightweight, and developer-friendly WordPress form builder plugin designed as a next-generation alternative to traditional contact form plugins.

It focuses on clean UI, performance, flexibility, and real-world usability â€” built with modern WordPress best practices.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- Drag & Drop Form Builder (Admin)
- Live Field Editing (Label, Placeholder, Default Value)
- AJAX-based Form Submission
- Secure Admin Actions (Nonce + Capability checks)
- Clean, modern UI inspired by Ogrodut design system
- Fully responsive (mobile-first)
- Lightweight & performance-focused
- Developer-friendly code structure

---

## ğŸ§© Supported Field Types

- Text
- Email
- Textarea
- Select
- Radio
- Checkbox
- Number
- Date
- Phone
- URL

---

## âš™ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** PHP (WordPress Plugin API)
- **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3, jQuery
- **Database:** WordPress DB (Custom Table)
- **Security:** WordPress Nonce, Capability checks
- **AJAX:** admin-ajax.php

